snippet.textDisplay: "Aayi Aayi" isn't just any song; it's about spreading peace and love. Listening to it gives you a warm and comforting feeling as you hear the beautiful story of Marvi. This song makes you want to visit and experience the rich culture of Sindh. It's a genuine representation of the region's traditions without any unnecessary stuff. Thank you, Coke Studio, for bringing this beautiful piece to life.
